BT /F1 13 Tf 50 534 Td (What PsyberShield Does) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 514 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 500 Td (PsyberShield helps you:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 486 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 472 Td (- scan a target URL) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 458 Td (- crawl in-scope pages) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 444 Td (- discover a local app target on a VPS when no URL is supplied) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 430 Td (- inspect local environment and server layout) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 416 Td (- generate safe fix artifacts) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 402 Td (- apply one real local fix lane with backup and validation) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 388 Td (- save reports, baselines, audit history, and comparison summaries) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 374 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 360 Td (PsyberShield is intentionally defensive:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 346 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 332 Td (- it warns before risky commands) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 318 Td (- it never prints secret values) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 304 Td (- it prefers read-only behavior unless you explicitly ask for fixes) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 290 Td (- it keeps a clear trail in the terminal and in saved outputs) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 276 Td () Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 50 262 Td (Command Map) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 242 Td () Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 228 Td (| Command | What it does | Typical use |) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 214 Td (| --- | --- | --- |) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 200 Td (| `scan` | Scans one target page or a discovered local target; supports browser-assisted login and `--profile` presets | Quick vulnerability check |) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 186 Td (| `crawl` | Crawls in-scope links across multiple pages; supports browser-assisted login and `--profile` presets | Broader site sweep |) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 172 Td (| `report` | Re-renders or previews a saved report | Review an existing JSON, Markdown, or HTML report |) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 158 Td (| `audit` | Shows the append-only audit trail | Review scans and fix events |) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50 144 Td (| `baseline` | Saves a scan snapshot for later comparison | Track a known-good state |) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
